Uses of Package
de.espirit.firstspirit.client.plugin

  • Packages that use de.espirit.firstspirit.client.plugin 
    Package Description
    de.espirit.firstspirit.client.plugin
    Provides interfaces and types for client plugins.

    This package provides types, interfaces and classes, that are to be used to integrate client plugins via the public hotspot of FirstSpirit.
    de.espirit.firstspirit.client.plugin.contextmenu
    Provides interfaces and types for java client context menu plugins.

    This package provides types, interfaces and classes, that are to be used to integrate client plugins via the public hotspot of FirstSpirit into the context menu of the java client.

    de.espirit.firstspirit.webedit.plugin.inlineedit
